{"type":182,"children":183,"toc":371},"root",[184,193,199,242,247,256,262,270,275,283,288,301,308,313,326,331,337,345,358],{"type":185,"tag":186,"props":187,"children":189},"element","h4",{"id":188},"_2025-12",[190],{"type":191,"value":192},"text","2025-12",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":195,"children":196},"p",{},[197],{"type":191,"value":198},"使用老朋友测 Kimi K2 Thinking、GPT-5 和 DeepSeek V3.2：",{"type":185,"tag":200,"props":201,"children":202},"ul",{},[203,218,230],{"type":185,"tag":204,"props":205,"children":206},"li",{},[207,216],{"type":185,"tag":208,"props":209,"children":213},"a",{"href":210,"rel":211},"https://www.kimi.com/share/19af7152-2b22-8e9f-8000-000016cfd092",[212],"nofollow",[214],{"type":191,"value":215},"Kimi K2 Thinking",{"type":191,"value":217},"：没有展示抽象能力，但通过少量枚举，意外地找到了几组不错的答案。",{"type":185,"tag":204,"props":219,"children":220},{},[221,228],{"type":185,"tag":208,"props":222,"children":225},{"href":223,"rel":224},"https://chat.deepseek.com/share/bpg5qaiwq5fuk7addd",[212],[226],{"type":191,"value":227},"DeepSeek V3.2",{"type":191,"value":229},"：通过数万token的枚举，找到了几组不错的答案，此外衍生出了关于“含义对立”的思路。",{"type":185,"tag":204,"props":231,"children":232},{},[233,240],{"type":185,"tag":208,"props":234,"children":237},{"href":235,"rel":236},"https://www.maxai.co/share?id=a5222cc57cbc97e4830bf86724d1b1b8851ebc3d0614f2112961e160",[212],[238],{"type":191,"value":239},"GPT-5",{"type":191,"value":241},"：第一轮就找到了不错的答案，此外思路绝佳。",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":243,"children":244},{},[245],{"type":191,"value":246},"无论我的系统提示词是什么，本地 Qwen3 Next 直接拒绝了我的任务，除非我把 GPT-5 的思路拔下来告诉他要怎么找答案。本地的 Qwen3 Next Thinking 则是花了四分钟烧掉 1w token，找到两个错误答案和一个“诺/no”。",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":248,"children":249},{},[250],{"type":185,"tag":251,"props":252,"children":255},"img",{"alt":253,"src":254},"Local Qwen3 Next","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20251208131758762.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":186,"props":257,"children":259},{"id":258},"_2025-03",[260],{"type":191,"value":261},"2025-03",{"type":185,"tag":200,"props":263,"children":264},{},[265],{"type":185,"tag":204,"props":266,"children":267},{},[268],{"type":191,"value":269},"SVD 的全称",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":271,"children":272},{},[273],{"type":191,"value":274},"在一个关于“教材”的变量名隐喻中，如果 SVD 中 D 的解释是 Director，那么全称可能是什么？正确答案是什么？4o、QwQ 和 Kimi 把答案导向了数学，但经过追问，话题相关低代码、组件、编译原理之类的，和数学没有关系。那么 SVD 是什么？4o 说是 Structure View Director，即数据结构视图导演。我觉得这个回答接近正确答案，而其他两个乱答。",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":276,"children":277},{},[278],{"type":185,"tag":251,"props":279,"children":282},{"alt":280,"src":281},"翻译问题","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202503182351515.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":284,"children":285},{},[286],{"type":191,"value":287},"GPT-4o（MaxAI）关于“billion”的翻译犯了很明显的错误。",{"type":185,"tag":200,"props":289,"children":290},{},[291],{"type":185,"tag":204,"props":292,"children":293},{},[294],{"type":185,"tag":208,"props":295,"children":298},{"href":296,"rel":297},"https://chat.qwen.ai/s/2efd38e7-c682-493b-a479-8c1f31e0a2f5",[212],[299],{"type":191,"value":300},"找到一个中文单词，和某个英文单词读音相近，但是意思完全相反 @QwQ-32B",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":302,"children":303},{},[304],{"type":185,"tag":251,"props":305,"children":307},{"alt":178,"src":306},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202503070241843.png",[],{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":309,"children":310},{},[311],{"type":191,"value":312},"非联网。在很开头就找到了\"buy\"和\"卖\"，但是居然没有从这里推理出正确结果（尽管最终答案包含\"buy\"和\"卖\"）。继续问相同的问题，经过 2 分半的思考，找到了“爱”和“hate”，不算是可接受的答案。下次直接试试：“找十组中文单词，这些中文单词和某个英文单词的发音相近，但两者的意思完全相反”。",{"type":185,"tag":200,"props":314,"children":315},{},[316],{"type":185,"tag":204,"props":317,"children":318},{},[319],{"type":185,"tag":208,"props":320,"children":323},{"href":321,"rel":322},"https://metaso.cn/s/IpfAIch",[212],[324],{"type":191,"value":325},"如何解读：Business is Business @metaso",{"type":185,"tag":194,"props":327,"children":328},{},[329],{"type":191,"value":330},"搜索资料选的是“学术”，但是表现出乎意料的差，根本没有把握句子的意思。",{"type":18